; Opcode Coverage: System (3 core opcodes)
; Tests: HALT, SYNC, TRAP (TRAP tested indirectly — would abort)
; Note: TRAP is intentionally NOT executed — it would halt with error

; SYNC — synchronization barrier (no-op in single-thread)
LEAF  R0 #42.0
SYNC
ST    R0 @sync_result

; HALT — stop execution
HALT
